snippet.title: PAC-MAN Geo playable Demo
snippet.description:
Features the Maps Gaming Platform.
In this version, PAC-MAN roams into the streets surrounding Moscone Center in San Francisco, CA.
This playable demo was created for GDC 2019 in close collaboration with Bandai Namco Studios. It also made it to NEXT '19 and Unite Sydney 2019.
